\overline{g(\boldsymbol{\theta})}^{IS} = \sum_{j=1}^M\left(g(\boldsymbol{\theta}^{(j)})w(\boldsymbol{\theta}^{(j)})\right) / \sum_{j=1}^M w(\boldsymbol{\theta}^{(j)}) \rightarrow^{a.s} E_p[g(\boldsymbol{\theta}|\mathbf{y})]
